subject: Dear Beneficiary
body:
Dear Beneficiary
Your $10.5 Million U.S dollars is available to be released to you if you can quickly get back to me for better briefing and instructions on how to receive your fund now
I'm waiting for your urgent response for the immediate processing now.
THANKS
Mr Roger Gorman

subject: Re: Dear Beneficiary
body:
Dear Mr. Roger Gorman,

Thank you for your message. I am interested in learning more about this opportunity. Could you please provide me with more details on how to proceed?

Best wishes,
Jeffrey
